# Cursor-Specific Features

_Rules for leveraging Cursor IDE's unique features, including keyboard shortcuts, AI assistance, and collaboration_

## Keyboard Shortcuts

**ID**: keyboard-shortcuts  
**Severity**: info  

Essential Cursor keyboard shortcuts to use

- Use `Cmd+Shift+P` (Mac) / `Ctrl+Shift+P` (Windows/Linux) for command palette
- Use `Cmd+K` (Mac) / `Ctrl+K` (Windows/Linux) for quick file navigation
- Use `F1` to show AI chat panel
- Use `Cmd+I` (Mac) / `Ctrl+I` (Windows/Linux) for inline AI completion
- Document custom shortcuts in project README

